    {
      "description": "Set up branch protection rules on `main` for clarity-house-press/wc-mcp.\\n\\n## Rules to apply (via `gh` CLI or GitHub rulesets API)\\n- Require PRs before merging\\n- Squash merge only\\n- Required status checks: `build`, `test`, `format`, `audit`, `CodeRabbit AI Code Review`\\n- Dismiss stale reviews on new commits\\n- Require conversation resolution before merge\\n- No bypass for admins\\n\\n## Acceptance Criteria\\n- Direct pushes to main are rejected\\n- PRs require all checks to pass\\n- Squash is the only merge strategy available",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-28T04:09:11.790Z",
      "source": "initial"
